Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,== OCR ==
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已經成為了神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮娜 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:48.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的裝甲服還可以維持多久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想也不會太長久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還可以回到上面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:02:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們看似還可以動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因為剛才爆炸的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實經已在高速衝向地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為地心吸力的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度會逐漸加快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…這是什麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你即是說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會像流星一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛烈地衝向地球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能 可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能  不要說笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼可行的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲正獨自奮力作戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉·亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那麼神氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是絲莉亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我是絲莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐 你又是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何許人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫布烈絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝霧·布烈絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫布烈絲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜歡這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在媽媽不在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是格拉·亞的記憶之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當格拉·亞還在絲莉亞腦內之時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類就是一種系統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受制於大腦的電子活動能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而作出反應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但情報是不會容許這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從絲莉亞腦袋衍生出來的就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在相反的事情卻發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在亞人的核心之內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所存在的異物\N-AntiSeed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是現在的布烈絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞人也會產生有害組織
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲的意識和布烈絲的肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是靠亞人有維繫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討…討厭呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才可以拯救她們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個地球的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然掌握在這班不懂禮貌的少女身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是令人發笑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 我想盡快令他們安頓下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去拯救她們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉 太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦才可以呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要怎麼辦才可安全著陸地球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包圍著我們的亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放你的枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞人將我改變呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮娜你也要想想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝甲服\N我也承認你那亞人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經在格拉·亞的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉·亞和我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正看著同樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉 蓮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 尚未完結
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還未…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你是截然不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,體內的異物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啟動免疫裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉·亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（燃料耗盡）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧  我的裝甲服…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會在此時沒燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氧氣都剩下這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非就此完結
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多些 多些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要多些力量呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚差…少許
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吩咐我辦事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我能力範圍之內
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎樣便怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像平日一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承認我的存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲 穿上我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MotosaLve
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為跟Skyhook\N碰撞而產生的衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令我失去了30%的機能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且燃料也不算那麼充裕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這方面 也想盡早了結此事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:12:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害 竟然可以這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 現在開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正打算摧毀你的神呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠使喚我的主人就是你\N布烈絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再說了 我不是那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞人竟想成為主宰人類的神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太妙想天開了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你堅持要保留人類
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若然人類以人類的身份存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:13:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意識和肉體都不會有進化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 我真的不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉·亞終於發瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 她正在助長自己的進化速度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲 有沒有大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起我 那麼你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一下子  燃料就耗盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MotosaLver 你會跟我\N拼到最後一刻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉·亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是人類給你的禮物呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:16:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MotosaLve
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 再生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神的印証
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到正確的進化方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲在我體內之時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在絲莉亞腦袋裡衍生我的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的存在已經永恆不變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是真正的同化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有東西的裡內也有我存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是真正的神形態
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很美呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘掉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空上出現數巨型微中子輻射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為尋求決策
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府立即組成考察團
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘗試去觀察此不明現象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想回家嗎
